{"tid":1011738,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［圍爐］有冇巴絲都覺得朋友拍拖之後會少咗半個朋友？","createTime":"2019-02-07T04:35:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-07T05:42:29.000Z","uid":88343,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6cd8c3f9d08e836a38ab820947bfbe432476616f","tid":1011738,"uid":88343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T04:35:26.000Z","msg":"豬年快樂先<br />\n<br />\n係，你冇睇錯，係半個朋友。朋友拍拖之後，好多嘢都會顧咗bf/gf先，出街、睇戲、食飯etc.<br />\n<br />\n佢又唔係完全唔會join以往圈子嘅聚，但時間上會難就咗、budget未必夠同未必吓吓都嚟到。<br />\n<br />\n例如有時想搵佢睇戲但佢通常都會同gf/bf睇，雖然佢哋有時會肯捱義氣睇多次，但又會覺得晒咗佢時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以佢哋有時肯同我睇戲我會好珍惜呢段時間。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔係想話佢哋重色輕友，佢哋都係人，都有自己嘅生活同選擇，純粹想圍吓爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e873bfb0982f4905ebbf9f19ce53fb53051e9189","tid":1011738,"uid":190387,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T05:06:33.000Z","msg":"就算點close點兄弟法 始終一有女就硬係會隔層野"},{"pid":"8ec2e50951973ab22bd7385f26bbf10db20c1b71","tid":1011738,"uid":88343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e873bfb0982f4905ebbf9f19ce53fb53051e9189","tid":1011738,"uid":190387,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T05:06:33.000Z","msg":"就算點close點兄弟法 始終一有女就硬係會隔層野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T05:35:12.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢叫埋女嚟又怕尷尬同做電燈膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18a24dfece2c301836e72d9f3fd9a8882faad255","tid":1011738,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T05:41:34.000Z","msg":"你都搵返個咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ceb16